duplicates-warning: De folowin existin {{PLURAL:$1|lexeem hab|lexeem dem hab}} de siem lema an langiwj kuod a de wan yu wan fu mek:
duplicates-instructions: A yu knuo dat {{PLURAL:$1|um|dey}} difran, klik de baax pan de bak'm a de fuom.
no-duplicate: Dis na wan duplikit a wan existin lexeem.
advanced-lexeme-id: Yu kyaan put wan lexeem ID fu aad faam dem fu wan existin lexeem insted a mekin wan nyuu wan. Put faam dem dat alredee exis pan de lexeem blienk, a dey go duplikiet!
advanced-partial-forms: Yu kyaan put som fuom dem blienk so dey no go put. Don go axisdentlee leebin owt eenee faam dem!
advanced-partial-forms-hint: To mek lexeem dem wid som fuom misin, go advaans.
description-with-forms-and-senses: $1, {{PLURAL:$2|0=no fuom|wan fuom|$2 fuom dem}} an {{PLURAL:$3|0=no sens|wan sens|$3 sens dem}}
bulk-first-field-not-lexeme-id: Sins de templet hab {{PLURAL:$1|wan faam|$1 farm dem}} an lain $4 a de taip-plies hab {{PLURAL:$2|wan feeld|$2 feeld dem}}, de firs feeld shud luk laik wan lexeem ID, but <q>$3</q> no luk laik wan lexeem ID. (Yu put wan faam tuu much een de taip-plies?)
bulk-first-field-lexeme-id: Sins de templet hab {{PLURAL:$1|wan fuom|$1 fuom dem}} an lain $4 a de taip-plies hab {{PLURAL:$2|wan feeld|$2 feeld dem}}, de firs feeld shud no luk laik wan lexeem ID, but <q>$3</q> luk laik wan. (Yu no put wan fuom?)
bulk-wrong-number-of-fields: Sins de templet hab {{PLURAL:$1|wan fuom|$1 fuom dem}}, ebree taip-plies lain shud wan (a) dat menee feeld dem (wen mekin wan nyuu lexeem) (b) wan muo (wen putin de ID a wan existin lexeem fu chienj), but lain $3 a de taip-plies hab {{PLURAL:$2|wan feel'|$2 feel' dem}} 'sted.
bulk-optional-forms-hint: A yu wan fu skip sam fuom dem, put dem a emptee (e.g. <kbd>...|||</kbd> fu chree emptee fuom dem a de en).
edit-general: Yu be een "chienj" muod. Chienjin de valyuu dung dey wil chienj, put a tek wie fuom dem a de min waant lexeem.
edit-mismatch-warning: Dis lexeem no mach dis templet! Pleez chek if dis de rait templet fu dis lexeem.

login-hint: Yu hafu [$1 laag een] befuo yu kyaan mek chienj dem wid dis chuul.
ambiguous-template: De templet $1 ded; om tek oba bai dis templet (dem):
